{"text_id":240781,"tokens":["How"," to"," Mour","n","\n\n","Know"," that"," everyone"," has"," their"," own"," unique"," experience"," with"," grief","."," Acknowledge"," that"," grief"," is"," a"," natural"," response"," to"," loss",","," and"," it","'","s"," okay"," to"," feel"," sad",","," angry",","," confused",","," or"," any"," other"," emotion"," that"," arises",".","\n\n","\"","Acknowledge"," that"," there"," are"," many"," kinds"," of"," loss","."," Loss"," can"," come"," in"," many"," forms",","," such"," as"," the"," death"," of"," a"," loved"," one",","," the"," end"," of"," a"," relationship",","," the"," loss"," of"," a"," job",","," or"," even"," the"," loss"," of"," a"," dream","."," Recognize"," that"," each"," loss"," is"," unique"," and"," can"," have"," a"," different"," impact"," on"," your"," life",".","\n\n","\"","Recognize"," that"," \u2018","stages","\u2019"," of"," mourning"," do"," not"," really"," exist","."," While"," many"," people"," have"," heard"," of"," the"," five"," stages"," of"," grief"," (","denial",","," anger",","," bargaining",","," depression",","," and"," acceptance","),"," research"," has"," shown"," that"," these"," stages"," are"," not"," universal"," and"," do"," not"," necessarily"," occur"," in"," a"," linear"," fashion","."," Grief"," is"," a"," complex"," and"," individualized"," process",","," and"," there"," is"," no"," one","-","size","-","fits","-","all"," approach"," to"," mourning",".","\n\n","\"","Dist","inguish"," between"," grief"," and"," mourning","."," Grief"," refers"," to"," the"," emotional"," response"," to"," loss",","," while"," mourning"," refers"," to"," the"," process"," of"," adapting"," to"," the"," loss"," and"," finding"," a"," way"," to"," live"," with"," it","."," Mourning"," is"," a"," social"," and"," cultural"," process"," that"," involves"," expressing"," your"," emotions"," and"," finding"," ways"," to"," honor"," your"," loss",".","\n\n","\"","Learn"," about"," the"," necessary"," \